Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望我的人在这儿多待一秒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want my men here one more second than they need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这东西有用  你就戴着了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If these worked, you'd be wearing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦西里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Vasily...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要有孩子了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're gonna have a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明不明白现在面临的状况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you have any idea what you're dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们会知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}People are going to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人会知道什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is everyone gonna hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何可能性都要追查下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to pursue every possibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管到底是谁的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}no matter who is to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这整个区域必须全面疏散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This entire region must be completely evacuated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要多少人手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How many men do you require?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约需要75万人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Approximately 750,000 men.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在撤离  你明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is an evacuation. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须跟我走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们下命令了  现在我来转告你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because they told me, so now I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里所有人都得走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everyone in this village, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不安全  空气中有辐射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not safe here. There's radiation in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么毛病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我多老了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know how old I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  很老吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know. Old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我82了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm 82.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一辈子都住在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've lived here my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里  那栋房子  就这地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right here, that house, this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我管安全不安全的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do I care about safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有任务  别给我找麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have a job. Don't cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是第一个扛枪站在这里的士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not the first soldier to stand here with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我12岁时  革命开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I was 12, the revolution came.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙皇的士兵  然后是布尔什维克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Czar's men. Then Bolsheviks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你这样的男孩  列队前进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Boys like you marching in lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们叫我们走  我不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They told us to leave. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是斯大林和他的饥荒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then there was Stalin and his famine,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌克兰大饥荒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the Holodomor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父母死了  两个姐妹死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My parents died. Two of my sisters died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们叫我们剩下的人走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They told the rest of us to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后二战爆发了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then the Great War.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德国人  俄罗斯人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}German boys. Russian boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多的士兵  饥荒和死尸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}More soldiers, more famine, more bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的兄弟们一去不回\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My brothers never came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我留下了  我现在还在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I stayed, and I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见识了那么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After all that I have seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道要现在走吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so I should leave now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为我根本看不到的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because of something I cannot see at all?
