Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家必须保守自己的机密  同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, the State must protect its secrets, Comrade.
