Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.87,0:23:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缺失的两页明显是有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The missing pages apparently refer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.72,0:23:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正空泡系数和AZ-5的内容\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to a positive void coefficient and AZ-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对你来说有什么意义吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does that mean anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.74,0:24:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目的是什么  你为什么问我这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you after here? Why are you asking me this?
