Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你是否意识到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And whether you realize it or not,
