Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.54,0:24:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底能不能帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you help me or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.34,0:24:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道这里写了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have no idea what would've gone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.10,0:24:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空泡系数和AZ-5没有任何关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Void coefficients have nothing to do with AZ-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.11,0:24:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  你可以走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There. Now you can go.
