Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.31,0:24:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得问对了问题就能得到真相吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think the right question will get you the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.65,0:24:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is no truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.04,0:24:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你怎么去问上级  得到的只有谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ask the bosses whatever you want and you'll get the lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.55,0:24:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我还是会吃枪子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I will get the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.30,0:26:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有两个规矩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I only have two rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.12,0:26:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.18,0:26:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要拿枪对着我  这个很简单  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't point this gun at me. That's easy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.49,0:26:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以拿枪对着那个蠢货\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can point it at this piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.07,0:26:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本无所谓  但不能对着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't give a fuck. Never me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.08,0:26:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.63,0:26:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你打了个动物  而它没有死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you hit an animal and it doesn't die,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.58,0:26:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续射击直到它死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}keep shooting until it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.63,0:26:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许让它们受罪  否则我就杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't let them suffer, or I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.33,0:26:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Understand?
