Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.66,0:32:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的第一次  是在阿富汗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My first time-- Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.15,0:32:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在穿过一栋房子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were moving through a house,
