Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.36,0:32:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真实的战争故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, that's a real war story.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.77,0:32:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不是电影里拍的那样美好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're never any good stories like in the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.77,0:32:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些破事儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.37,0:32:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人站在那儿  砰  打中腹部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A man was there-- boom, stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.08,0:32:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕  那天接下来的时间里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was so scared. I didn't pull the trigger again
