Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.09,0:32:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想  "就这样了  巴乔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought, "Well, that's it, Bacho.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.38,0:32:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开枪打中了人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"You put a bullet in someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.83,0:33:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不再是原来的你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"You're not you anymore.
