Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.54,0:33:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而第二天早晨醒来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But then you wake up the next morning,
