Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.60,0:38:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让他们听见  我想让他们全都听见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want them to hear! I want them to hear it all!
