Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.40,0:38:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉那些天才他们都干了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell those geniuses what they have done!
