Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.99,0:38:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们  去告诉他们  雷日科夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell them! Go tell them! Ryzhkov!
