Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.41,0:39:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们给出的是对外宣称的数值\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They gave them the propaganda number.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.83,0:39:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个机器人本就没用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That robot was never going to work.
