Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.78,0:40:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也许可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We could-- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.16,0:40:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以把熔化的铅从空中倒下来  像涂层一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We could melt it and pour it from above, like a coating.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.58,0:40:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先  我们手头的铅已经快用完了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First of all, we've already used most of the lead we had--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.00,0:40:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-为了裹住  -其他反应堆厂房的仪器上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- to line the... - There's lead sheeting around the instruments
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.79,0:40:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有铅层\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the other reactor buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.67,0:40:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵们正剥下来  用在防护服上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The soldiers are stripping it for their armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.34,0:40:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.59,0:40:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使可以  我们还得把熔化的金属放在直升机里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even if, we're still talking about boiling metal in a helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.18,0:41:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是铅  鲍里斯  重得很\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it's lead, Boris, it'll weight a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.23,0:41:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把石墨射进洞里怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What if we shoot the graphite into the hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.06,0:41:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有大口径的子弹  爆炸子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've got high-caliber bullets, exploding bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.52,0:41:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种子弹不会反弹  而是会推动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They wouldn't just ricochet, they'd push--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.69,0:41:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想往暴露在外的核反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You wanna shoot exploding bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.86,0:41:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射爆炸子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at an exposed nuclear reactor?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.74,0:41:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这个嘛  -不不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Well... - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.20,0:41:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再去把楼顶点着火吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's go light that roof back on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.29,0:41:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次扑灭得太轻松了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was so easy to put out the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.67,0:41:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到底在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are we talking about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.29,0:41:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要新的机器人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need another robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.34,0:41:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一台可以承受辐射的机器人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One that can withstand the radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.34,0:41:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问过了  没有这样的机器人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've asked. There is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.84,0:41:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国货呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Americans?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.85,0:41:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果美国有这种科技\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the Americans had that kind of technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.77,0:41:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他们会给我们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}do you really think they'd give it to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.64,0:41:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使他们真的有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And even if they would,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.43,0:41:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央委员会也不会屈膝请求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the Central Committee will never stoop to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.48,0:41:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我都心知肚明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know it, I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.31,0:41:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有机器人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are no robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.61,0:41:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生物机器人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Biorobots.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.08,0:42:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.29,0:42:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们用生物机器人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We use biorobots.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.55,0:42:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.47,0:43:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天碰见了很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A lot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.02,0:43:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们从哪找到食物的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where do they get their food?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.36,0:43:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们吃鸡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They eat the chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.27,0:43:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后互相吞食\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then they eat each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.50,0:44:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挨家挨户搜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Door-to-door.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.11,0:45:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕沃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pavel?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.53,0:45:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕沃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pavel!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.67,0:45:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听不到吗  我在跟你说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't hear me? I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.63,0:45:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.06,0:45:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.36,0:45:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.40,0:48:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs29\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H364845&\blur0\fad(0,2000)\c&HFDFEFD&\pos(191.2,147.006)}1986年10月
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.24,0:48:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵同志们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.99,0:48:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏维埃人民已经受够了这场事故\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the Soviet people have had enough of this accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.99,0:49:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们希望我们收拾好残局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They want us to clean this up,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.49,0:49:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将这项艰巨的任务托付于你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we have entrusted you with this serious task.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.75,0:49:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴于作业区域的性质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because of the nature of the working area,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.54,0:49:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们每人只有不到90秒的时间进行作业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you will each have no more than 90 seconds to solve this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.67,0:49:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真听好我的每一条指示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Listen carefully to each of my instructions,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.55,0:49:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并严格服从\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and do exactly as you have been told.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.22,0:49:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了你自身安全  以及你战友的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is for your own safety and the safety of your comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.72,0:49:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要进入3号反应堆厂房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will enter Reactor Building Three,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.31,0:49:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上楼后不要直接前往屋顶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}climb the stairs but do not immediately proceed to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.06,0:49:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到达顶楼后  先在室内等候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When you get to the top, wait inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.23,0:49:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在去往屋顶的入口处喘口气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}behind the entrance to the roof and catch your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.23,0:49:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为后续的工作做好准备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will need it for what comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.94,0:49:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是作业区域  我们必须将石墨清理干净\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the working area. We must clear the graphite.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.03,0:49:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些石墨成块状\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some of it is in blocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.12,0:49:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重量大约四十到五十公斤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}weighing approximately 40 to 50 kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.58,0:49:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须将它们从屋顶这边投下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They all must be thrown over the edge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.25,0:49:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你们的同志们正快速通过入口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Watch your comrades moving fast from this opening,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.67,0:49:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后左转\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then turning to the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.25,0:49:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入作业区域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and entering the workspace here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.59,0:49:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心不要绊倒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take care not to stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.88,0:49:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屋顶上有个洞  小心不要掉进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a hole in the roof. Take care not to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.26,0:49:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,务必快速行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will need to move quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.55,0:49:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万分小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you will need to move carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.80,0:50:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听完我的描述  清楚你们的任务了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you understand your mission as I have described it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.31,0:50:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  大将同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, Comrade General.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.39,0:50:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们人生中最重要的90秒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the most important 90 seconds of your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.94,0:50:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将任务牢记于心  然后着手工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commit your task to memory, then do your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.28,0:50:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该出发了  90秒之后  我会拉响警铃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's time to go. After 90 seconds, I will ring a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.45,0:51:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到铃声  你们立刻返回\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When you hear it, return immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.41,0:51:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将铲子丢进垃圾桶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}drop your shovels in the bin,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.45,0:51:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沿走廊一直走去进行消毒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and proceed down the hallway for decontamination.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.49,0:51:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是  在屋顶时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Above all, while on the roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.12,0:51:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将残骸扔出护栏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}throw your debris over the rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.70,0:51:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要向护栏外看  明白没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do not look over the rail. Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.75,0:51:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.17,0:51:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我口令  准备  出发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On my mark. Ready. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.72,0:53:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵同志们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Comrade soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.56,0:53:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.11,0:53:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.82,0:53:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your glove!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.48,0:54:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mommy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.09,0:54:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs25\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H364845&\blur0\fad(0,0)\c&HFDFEFD&\pos(191.2,151.915)}普里皮亚季\N{\fs22}1986年12月
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.67,0:55:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉让你来这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry for all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.13,0:55:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们需要和你谈谈  而且没有...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we needed to speak to you somewhere without...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.30,0:55:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要审判迪亚特洛夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're going to put Dyatlov on trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.10,0:55:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有布卡诺夫和福明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and Bryukhanov and Fomin.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.18,0:55:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会被传唤  作为专家证人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're going to be asked to give expert testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.10,0:55:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三个都要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.69,0:55:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这是...在庭审之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that's-- Before that happens--
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.44,0:55:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央委员会让列加索夫去维也纳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Central Committee is sending Legasov to Vienna.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.78,0:55:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是国际原...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's the headquarters of the International--
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.91,0:55:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国际原子能机构的总部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Atomic Energy Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.20,0:55:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  这我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, I know what's in Vienna.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.16,0:55:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们让你干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are they asking you to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.50,0:56:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉全世界发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell the world what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.46,0:56:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你最好知道发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, then you better know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.84,0:56:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我构建了一条时间线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've constructed a timeline,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.80,0:56:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以每分钟为单位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}minute by minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.84,0:56:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的地方以秒为单位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Second by second in some places.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.85,0:56:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一项决定  按下的每一个按钮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every decision, every button push,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.68,0:56:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开关的每一次通断\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}every turn of a switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.85,0:56:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢  他们有罪吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And? Are they guilty?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.64,0:56:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.27,0:56:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严重失职  违反安全规定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of gross incompetence, violation of safety regulations,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.28,0:56:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的鲁莽简直难以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}recklessness beyond belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.61,0:56:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是爆炸呢  我不确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But the explosion? I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.45,0:56:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫你不确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you mean you're not sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.32,0:56:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我分析了数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've analyzed the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.49,0:56:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托普特诺夫说的是实话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Toptunov was telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.91,0:56:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们关闭了反应堆  然后就爆炸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They shut the reactor down, and then it exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.63,0:56:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这篇文章可能会有答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think this article may have the answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.09,0:56:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其中的两页被人撕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but two pages have been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.01,0:56:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前看过这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.10,0:57:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请相信我这话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please, believe me when I tell you that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.89,0:57:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不知道这会导致爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had no idea it could cause an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.31,0:57:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们当时都不知道  -你们都不知道什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- None of us knew. - None of you knew what?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.69,0:57:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1975年  列宁格勒的一座RBMK反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In 1975, in an RBMK reactor in Leningrad,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.20,0:57:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条燃料管道破裂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a fuel channel ruptured.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.16,0:57:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操作员按下AZ-5按钮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The operators pressed AZ-5,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.99,0:57:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但功率并没有马上下降\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but instead of the power going down immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.04,0:57:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是在极短时间内上升了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for a brief moment it went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.21,0:57:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.62,0:57:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的一位同事沃科夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, this was the very question posed
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.04,0:57:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就提出了这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}by a colleague of mine named Volkov.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.13,0:57:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是这篇文章的作者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's the one who wrote this article.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.30,0:57:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RBMK型反应堆在低功率下运行时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When an RBMK reactor runs at low power,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.30,0:57:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,状态相当不稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's notoriously unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.17,0:57:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,易发生反应性波动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Prone to swings in reactivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.39,0:57:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Under normal circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.89,0:57:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制棒可以弥补这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the control rods can compensate for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.85,0:57:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Under normal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.14,0:57:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切尔诺贝利工作人员在测试期间降低了反应堆功率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Chernobyl staff stalled the reactor during the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.94,0:57:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了恢复电力  他们几乎把\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They pulled almost all the control rods out
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.77,0:57:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有控制棒都拔出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to bring the power back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.94,0:57:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是沃科夫在列宁格勒发现的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is what Volkov learned from Leningrad.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.65,0:57:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当硼控制棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the boron control rods
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.07,0:57:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全从反应堆中抽出后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are completely withdrawn from the reactor,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.82,0:57:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再放回去时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when they're put back in,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.07,0:58:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最先接触堆芯的不是硼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the first thing that enters the core isn't boron.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.24,0:58:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是石墨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's graphite.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.83,0:58:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制棒尖端是石墨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The control rods have graphite tips
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.21,0:58:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会置换水和蒸汽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that displace water and steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.71,0:58:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此反应功率不会降低\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So the reactivity doesn't go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.00,0:58:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相反会急剧上升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It goes up dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.26,0:58:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们为什么要按下那个按钮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why on Earth would they press that button?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.26,0:58:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.64,0:58:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔科夫提醒过克里姆林宫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Volkov warned the Kremlin,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.31,0:58:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是十年前了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.60,0:58:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但苏联核工业领域的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But there could be no doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.36,0:58:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对霸权是不容置疑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about the supremacy of the Soviet nuclear industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.40,0:58:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克格勃将其列为国家机密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The KGB classified it as a state secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.41,0:58:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我看到反应堆被炸开时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I saw the reactor blown open,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.74,0:58:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍不认为会是AZ-5的缺陷导致的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I still didn't think it could be this flaw in AZ-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.46,0:58:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个缺陷不会导致爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because the flaw will not lead to an explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.79,0:58:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非操作人员已把反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}unless the operators have pushed the reactor
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.75,0:58:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推向了灾难边缘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to the edge of disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.80,0:58:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-所以是他们的错吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- So it is their fault? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.68,0:59:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不全是他们的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not only their fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.10,0:59:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.76,0:59:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算在维也纳也这么说吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that what you're going to say in Vienna?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.60,0:59:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会那么天真吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't possibly be that naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.82,0:59:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前整个苏联有16个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are 16 RBMK reactors
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.74,0:59:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RBMK型反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}running in the Soviet Union right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.61,0:59:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须整改它们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to fix them.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.78,0:59:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的办法就是公开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The only way to do that is to go public,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.66,0:59:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迫使中央委员会采取行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}force the Central Committee to take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.75,0:59:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样做会让列加索夫羞辱一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What you're proposing is that Legasov humiliate a nation
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.83,0:59:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能忍受羞辱的国家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that is obsessed with not being humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.79,0:59:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以和克格勃谈条件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can make a deal with the KGB.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.38,0:59:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去维也纳时不要提及这事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll leave this information out in Vienna,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.67,0:59:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克格勃会私下让我们修好剩下的反应堆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they quietly let us fix the remaining reactors.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.63,0:59:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和克格勃谈条件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A deal with the KGB?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.01,0:59:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还说我天真\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I'm "naive."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.26,0:59:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会盯上你的家人  你的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll go after your family, they'll go after your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.77,0:59:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有机会向全世界发声  瓦列利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have a chance to talk to the world, Valery.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.60,0:59:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我有这个机会...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If that chance was mine--
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.44,0:59:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你没有这个机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it isn't, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.40,0:59:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识比你更勇敢的人  霍缪克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've know braver souls than you, Khomyuk.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.65,1:00:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人拥有机会却最终什么都没做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Men who had their moment and did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.91,1:00:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一旦涉及到你和你所爱的人的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because when it's your life and the lives of everyone you love,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.08,1:00:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的道德信念就一文不值了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}your moral conviction doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.70,1:00:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被你抛诸脑后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It leaves you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.08,1:00:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候你脑中只有不想被枪毙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And all you want at that moment is not to be shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.63,1:00:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道瓦西里·伊格纳滕科这个名字吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know the name Vasily Ignatenko?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.84,1:00:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.72,1:00:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是一名消防员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was a fireman.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.72,1:00:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在爆炸后两周死去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He died two weeks after the accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.98,1:00:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看望过他的遗孀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been looking in on his widow.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.77,1:00:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她生下了遗腹子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She gave birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.61,1:00:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.27,1:00:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子挣扎了四个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The baby lived for four hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.78,1:00:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说那个母亲遭受的辐射量原本足以致死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They said the radiation would have killed the mother,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.53,1:00:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却被腹中的孩子吸收了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but the baby absorbed it instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.28,1:00:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Her baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.45,1:00:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们生活的国家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We live in a country
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.04,1:00:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们要替母亲去死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where children have to die to save their mothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.92,1:00:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的条件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To hell with your deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.00,1:01:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管我们会怎样呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And to hell with our lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.05,1:01:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得有人说出真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone has to start telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.48,1:01:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜各位同志们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Congratulations, comrades.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.94,1:01:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是3828人中的最后一批\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are the last of 3,828 men.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.95,1:01:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们出色地履行了自己的职责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have performed your duties perfectly.
